  "title": "Indigenous life expectancy in Sweden 1850-1899: Towards a long and healthy life?",
  "abstract": "Previous research has shown that the health transition and demographical pattern of indigenous people has followed a different path compared to non-indigenous groups living in the same area with higher mortality rates and shortened life expectancy at birth",
